@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@token = Bearer TOKENNI_SHU_YERGA_QOYING
@productId = 1
@departmentId = 1


### Login - javobdan tokenni yuqoridagi @token ga qo'ying
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "muhammad",
  "password": "12345678"
}


### Product bo'yicha bo'lim narxlari
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}/department-prices
Authorization: {{token}}


### Product bo'yicha hamma bo'lim narxlarini saqlash (super_admin/admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}/department-prices
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prices": [
    { "department_id": 1, "price_per_unit": 2000, "is_active": true },
    { "department_id": 2, "price_per_unit": 8000, "is_active": true },
    { "department_id": 3, "price_per_unit": 5000, "is_active": true },
    { "department_id": 4, "price_per_unit": 1500, "is_active": true }
  ]
}


### Bitta bo'lim narxini yangilash (super_admin/admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}/department-prices/{{departmentId}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price_per_unit": 2500,
  "is_active": true
}
